1. *Istoriju* moramo da naučimo (We have to learn the history).
2. To je deo *istorije* naše zemlje (That is part of the history of our country).
3. Oni su činili *istoriju* (They made history).
4. *Istoriju* možemo da menjamo (We can change history).
5. On je čitao knjigu o *istoriji* (He was reading a book about history).
6. Oni školuju decu o *istoriji* (They school children about history).
7. Nastavnici uče decu o *istoriji* (Teachers teach children about history).
8. U ovom gradu ima mnogo znamenitosti iz *istorije* (In this city there are many historic sites).